trans-unit.source: Represents a cell in a table.

trans-unit.source: Only a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableRowStructure> can be the parent of a TableCellStructure.

trans-unit.target: Lägger till ett underordnat objekt till den <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
trans-unit.target: Den här medlemmen är en implementering för medlem av explicit gränssnitt.

trans-unit.source: It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IAddChild> interface.
trans-unit.target: Det kan användas endast när den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure>instans omvandlas till ett <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IAddChild>gränssnitt.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.IAddChild> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure>

trans-unit.source: Every <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure> must have at least one child.
trans-unit.target: Varje <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure>måste ha minst en underordnad.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableCellStructure>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a child is a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ParagraphStructure>, but it can be a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ListStructure>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.FigureStructure>, or a (nested) <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableStructure>.
trans-unit.target: En underordnad är vanligtvis en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ParagraphStructure>, men det kan vara en <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ListStructure>, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.FigureStructure>, eller en (kapslade) <xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableStructure>.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.TableStructure> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.FigureStructure> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ListStructure> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.DocumentStructures.ParagraphStructure>
